    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with everything so it\u2019s ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a dependable car that looks great on the road, this is the one! Come take it for a spin!",
