    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance is documented, including a rod bearing service and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement plates to mitigate common floor pan fatigue. Suspension dynamics are sharpened via Bilstein B16 coilovers and refreshed control arm bushings. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains tight with linear power delivery and exceptional throttle response. A mechanically sorted driver's car optimized for performance enthusiasts.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Maintained regularly. Clean title. Runs well. Solid interior. Ready for immediate use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
