    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for this absolute gem of a car. It's been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really wonderful shape, running smoothly and ready for all your upcoming adventures! I've taken great care of it, and I think you're going to love how it handles. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
