      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the robust 3.6L M96 flat-six, benefiting from VarioCam Plus for an optimized torque curve across the rev range. The G96 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, mechanical engagement, paired with a rear-drive layout for classic 911 dynamics. Recent service includes a borescope inspection showing clean cylinder walls and an updated IMS bearing for peace of mind. The chassis retains its composure with firm damping and precise turn-in, though minor cosmetic patina reflects its honest driver status. A mechanically sound example ready for the apex.",
